StarkNet is the most promising and advanced L2 on Ethereum. Unlike other L2s, StarkNet is not EVM-compatible and writes contracts in Cairo.

Other L2s sacrificed long-term benefits for short-term gains by forcing to be EVM-compatible and sticking with Solidity.
